

- Task 1: Develop a class (QuizCLI) that manages the command line interface for
the user to complete different quizzes and perform other quiz related actions.

- Task 2: Develop a class (UserAnswers) that will record and manage a history of
the user's cumulative scores over different categories.

- Task 3: Develop a class (QuizSessionReview) that will keeps track of the
user's responses in a session, allowing the user to see explanations of their
incorrectly answered questions.